    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方祈妖录》是一款2.5D像素动作肉鸽游戏。这是一个芙兰朵露的冒险故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/b0e936f3ca99f5402a50910fa21c9e8a.avif?t=1767177750\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏，你能体验的爽快的战斗，及对敌人反击的快感。这是是一款只需要操作一把近战武器，就能体验各种各样技能的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以靠击败敌人来触发技能，也可以对敌方技能进行回击，然后产生新的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/0b98803d94240d2c6c4f3f8c8c247120.poster.avif?t=1767177750\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/0b98803d94240d2c6c4f3f8c8c247120.webm?t=1767177750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/0b98803d94240d2c6c4f3f8c8c247120.mp4?t=1767177750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是击败触发的符卡技能，还是回击的敌方的技能，你都可以靠强化卡，对它们进行改变，让整个游戏体验变得更加丰富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人的近战攻击也会和你近战产生弹反效果，让战斗交互性有了很大的提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/f8f990189ff1ce421768222e367fa619.poster.avif?t=1767177750\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/f8f990189ff1ce421768222e367fa619.webm?t=1767177750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/f8f990189ff1ce421768222e367fa619.mp4?t=1767177750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏通关的机制也非常特别，你不需要全部打败他们，可以按自己策略选择需要击败的敌人，这样将会大幅提升你的战斗效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/0478288f1129cd1eb13ee9dc0fdaa86a.poster.avif?t=1767177750\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/0478288f1129cd1eb13ee9dc0fdaa86a.webm?t=1767177750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/0478288f1129cd1eb13ee9dc0fdaa86a.mp4?t=1767177750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景互动元素也非常丰富，你可以爽快的攻击甚至破坏它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏进度的推进，你也可以解锁更多的功能卡，让游戏玩法变得更加丰富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来加入这个奇妙的幻想乡，进行一个刺激爽快的冒险吧！！</p>",
